Summary: Translators is a library which aims to bring free, multiple, enjoyable translation to individuals and students in Python. It based on the translation interface of Google, Microsoft(Bing), Baidu, Alibaba, Tencent, NetEase(Youdao), Sogou, Deepl, etc.
